{"id":"pas-dammim","term":"Pas-dammim","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The border of blood = Ephes-dammim (q.v.), between Shochoh and Azekah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 17:1\">1 Sam. 17:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:13\">1 Chr. 11:13</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Samuel 17:1","1 Chronicles 11:13"]}